  <source>Wayne State University</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study was to investigate the presence of neuroinflammation in children
      with infantile spasms using 11C-PK11195 positron emission tomography (PK PET) scan, and its
      response to ACTH treatment by repeating the PK PET scan after treatment.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
